{"tid":1810750,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"小米攝影機影到人地屋企，Google緊急暫停合作","createTime":"2020-01-04T06:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T07:01:05.000Z","uid":174512,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4bd7c2d3fbbf26b5bb27ec5fe63d28745fe631","tid":1810750,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:46:00.000Z","msg":"#小米攝影機拍到別人家<br />\n#Google緊急暫停合作<br />\n<br />\n許多人會購買智慧攝影機觀察家中的小孩或寵物，小米米家智慧攝影機最近被發現嚴重漏洞，打開監視功能卻看到陌生人家中的影像，Google在接獲回報後，第一時間暫停與米家的整合協作。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，最先是美國一名Reddit論壇用戶「u/Dio-V」發現這項漏洞，他將米家智慧攝影機連結到Google Nest Hub，顯示出的影像並非自己家中，而是別人家一名在椅子上睡覺的人，以及嬰兒在床上睡覺的靜止影像。「u/Dio-V」確實表明使用的是米家1080p智慧攝影機，並與Google Nest Hub相互連結。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle發言人迅速做出回應，表示已經知道這項問題，並正在與小米聯繫以進行修復，同時小米硬體設備禁止授權訪問Google Nest Hub、Assistant，直到這項問題被解決為止。小米則說，總部目前正在了解情形中。<br />\n<br />\n轉摘：LTN NEWS<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8hTxYf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8hTxYf.png&h=e69ed543&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"208549c7e29bec611590c259efbcdee4515c1bd7","tid":1810750,"uid":174512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"屋企有小米嘅任何產品好快啲換啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17a1db84db6b27dcb2430f40849ba72bd20a101","tid":1810750,"uid":174512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:47:58.000Z","msg":"中共可以睇到你打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc11e8df103854eec15cfc420403ecb7ab7f067","tid":1810750,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:48:58.000Z","msg":"傳說中的backdoor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61620f99d032ecae9a3448323ca49fcf71345b79","tid":1810750,"uid":136543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e17a1db84db6b27dcb2430f40849ba72bd20a101","tid":1810750,"uid":174512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2